# Grid Box Configuration

The docking grid center was determined from the co-crystallized ligand (E20) present in the original 4EY7 structure.

## PyMOL Commands

```pymol
select ligand, resn E20
print(cmd.centerofmass("ligand"))
```

Output:

```text
[-1.6241149361476006, -50.09128532940734, 2.0558886275481623]
```

## Grid Center Coordinates

```text
center_x = -1.624
center_y = -50.091
center_z = 2.056
```

## Grid Size

